2011-04-23: Sparked 0.10
------------------------

New features:
 - sparked.web.util - Utility module for twisted.web - simple
   uploading files and wrapping HTTP authentication.


2011-04-22: Sparked 0.9.13
------------------------

Bugfixes:
 - sparked.web.io - When connection fails, javascript now keeps retrying periodically.


2011-04-18: Sparked 0.9.12
------------------------

Features:
 - sparked.application - StateMachine now has an events object to listen to state changes

Bugfixes:
 - sparked.tap - use blocking resolver to work around DNS resolution issues
 - add current directory when importing sparked module (unless root)
 - add *.js to package_data to fix Pypi package


2011-04-15: Sparked 0.9.11
------------------------

Bugfixes:
 - sparked.web.io - fix for including multiple script tags
 - add current directory when importing sparked module (unless root)


2011-04-13: Sparked 0.9.10
------------------------

New features:
 - sparked.web.io - longpolling based messaging between python and javascript


2011-03-20: Sparked 0.9.10
------------------------

Bugfixes:
 - do not crash when importing dbus module fails, but show a warning instead.
